        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. 12V battery removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R002224",
          "label": "12V battery removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Reserve tank removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582729_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. 12V battery base removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582730_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Transmission Support"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Lay down a bracing plate on the transmission and support it with a garage jack."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Transmission mount assy. removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582731_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the harness cover (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582732_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Remove the ground cable (A) and remove the transmission mount assembly."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Transmission mount assembly."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582733_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Tighten the new transmission mount mounting bolts (A). Temporarily tighten the new transmission mount bracket mounting bolt/nut (B) and loosen the transmission mount bracket mounting bolt (C). Install the ground cable (D). Remove the garage jack."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582734_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "Install the harness cover (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Transmission Mount Tightening"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582735_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Raise the car body using a lift. Loosen the torque rod mounting bolt (A). Lower the vehicle body."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582736_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "4",
      "text": "Tighten the transmission mount bracket mounting bolts/nuts in numerical order. Raise the car body using a lift."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582737_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "6",
      "text": "Tighten the mounting bolts on the torque rod."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Front Under Cover Installation",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000850",
          "label": "Front Under Cover Installation",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. 12V Battery Base Mounting"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "358_3.0_jpn_11582738_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
